Package: onet2r
Title: Access O*NET Web Services API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alex", "Farach", email = "alex@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R client for the O*NET Web Services API 2.0. Provides functions
    to search occupations, retrieve occupation details (skills, knowledge,
    abilities), access database tables, and perform taxonomy crosswalks.
    All functions return tibbles for easy integration with tidyverse workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
